> We're well past our point of gathering anything useful from this world.
> They are too numerous and too well supported for us to pull off any level of
> alteration to the timeline safely.  Better to leave this mudball and return
> to Cybertron and ready for the next phase."
>
> The gauntlet was thrown then, seeing how much was risen tot he bait DINOBOT
> threw out.  "Endless little skirmishes over the timeline that never go
> anywhere.  Disruptions caused to casuality that cannot be undone.  We are
> better to go to our own ponit of origin and use our knowledge to our
> advantage and stop skirmishing with a superior enemy."

<NEW>

It was ANTAGONY that looked over at DINOBOT her optics narrowed,
"Don't you get it?" She stalked towards him, "Your precious little
timeline may already be changed. Your Cybertron may no longer exist!"

TARANTULUS stood up, "What do you mean, speak quickly my patience is
wearing thin."

ANTAGONY glanced back at TARANTULUS and then back at SKYSHADOW and
DINOBOT "I don't mean that Cybertron is gone . . " She paused for a
moment and smiled as if that thought amused her, and then she
continued "But I mean that the Cybertron that you knew may have
changed."

There was a startled look from TARANTULUS as he frantically began
typing a message into one of his companels next to him, apparently
trying to contact someone on CYBERTON.

"And I take it that if we won't to make any changes back then we need
to be the first to reach it." SKYSHADOW said calmly.

ANTAGONY turned to look at SKYSHADOW with dark optics and then nodded.

(TAG)

- Preston
